=====
 ALL 
=====
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license: Public Domain
:doc created at: Sun Jan  4 21:03:56 2009
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

allow commands to be executed by all users

| 

  register all .py files 

| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *all-add*

    :description: add command to be allowed by all users

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !all-add version
        <output> version command is now allowed for all clients


2) *all-list*

    :description: list commands allowed by all users

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !all-list
        <output> version


3) *all-del*

    :description: remove command from the allowed list

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !all-del version
        <output> version command is removed from allowed list


